lead_paragraph: Juan Martin del Potro is the lowest-ranked man to reach the U.S. Open quarterfinals since Jimmy Connors in 1991, and it turns out a 27-year-old Argentine can share much in common with a 39-year-old American.

headline.print_headline: Del Potro Back in US Open Quarterfinals After Thiem Retires
